{"tid":1074321,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"第一神拳而家真係好撚垃圾","createTime":"2019-03-23T10:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T09:07:52.000Z","uid":173852,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"0a8da4af3a4b191be8ae1ff5743b2a1e9dda61c7","tid":1074321,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:08:36.000Z","msg":"(個post想出好耐 而家講可能都嫌old new左)<br />\n<br />\n小學追到出黎做野 <br />\n睇住一步由廢柴打到拳王 鷹村拎世界冠軍 青木木村雖然唔係頂尖但仍然努力奮鬥 熱血到仆街<br />\n成套野就算去到70幾期都重有一步vs澤村依d超好睇既比賽<br />\n打完唐澤 直頭覺得一步係成熟左啦 可以再進一步<br />\n點知之後無得打官田 都算<br />\n打班亞洲佬又淨返鎖血狗衝 之前學既野無撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打打下又輸撚左 一輸又咩退出 退出都唔撚完 又養新人 屌你老母<br />\n真係寧願佢鎖血打贏世界拳王完撚左算 就算垃圾都叫有個尾丫<br />\n而家次次睇佢更新真係都眼撚冤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a82ba096792a09090021a8f34ae64262f244d0","tid":1074321,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:09:50.000Z","msg":"有好過？"},{"pid":"b0b6785b4ad3999ba89c0ff403fc509870a55023","tid":1074321,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"35a82ba096792a09090021a8f34ae64262f244d0","tid":1074321,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:09:50.000Z","msg":"有好過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:00:25.000Z","msg":"交到70集貨wor"},{"pid":"e74cc2adc57373a83a4adcf9b6ee1fc327c36503","tid":1074321,"uid":139456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:17:34.000Z","msg":"一早已經放棄左呢套野"},{"pid":"f632b8fc304e8cdff3d7dbb8de5720628bb50e60","tid":1074321,"uid":35451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:30:58.000Z","msg":"之前好似睇到一步輸比世界第2<br />\n之後都冇更新了"},{"pid":"8edb4e7d41300111568b260000b04573b01433e0","tid":1074321,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:47:08.000Z","msg":"打嗰堆東南亞拳皇開始愈嚟愈垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完依個post望下最近生肉，搞咩一步變咗光頭<im